      <title>消息人士称，高盛取消了欧盟时代英国顶级银行家的奖金上限</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-scraps-eu-era-bonus-cap-top-bankers-uk-source-says-2024-05-02/</link>
